First of all,
we are developing the system for general public of any age, so it should be easy to acess, easy to use system.

our main goal is to provide easier way to book the ticket system to stop the long waiting of physical queuing

some basic requirements for the system is (it may change in the future devlopments):

1. welcome and the sarting of the app info
2. option running movies or upcoming movies
3. running movies
   currently runnign movies
   upcoming movies
   what movies are going to be released
4. chose option in running movies
5. shows availabel seats
6. user gives the input of the seat they like
7. ask if they want to book it or cancel
   if booked then provide booking with details
   orelse
   just goto step 2
